description: Location, location, location. This 1-bedroom condo is close to everything. Restaurants, shopping, and the beach are only minutes away. The condo itself has an open and bright living space. Enjoy your evenings on the large deck or take it inside and entertain by the fireplace. There are hardwood floors in the main living area. The bedroom has a California closet system. The kitchen had beautiful granite counters, tile floors, and a new dishwasher. There is a shared washer and dryer in the basement that the association pays for. The unit has a new water heater (2019). The building had a new roof installed in 2013. Each unit has its own individual storage in the basement.
